Privacy Notice
Effective Date: October 19, 2024

Glitched Fox Studios ("we," "us," or "our") is committed to protecting the privacy of our users. This Privacy Notice explains how we collect, use, and disclose information from users of our software and associated services (the "Product"). By using our Product, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this Privacy Notice.

1. Information We Collect
We may collect and process the following types of information:

Personal Information: Information you provide directly to us, such as your name, email address, or other contact details, when creating an account, subscribing to our newsletter, or contacting customer support.
Usage Data: Information automatically collected when using the Product, including but not limited to IP addresses, device information, and usage patterns.
Cookies and Tracking Technologies: We may use cookies and similar tracking technologies to monitor activity on our Product and store certain information.
2. How We Use Your Information
We may use the information we collect to:

Provide, maintain, and improve the Product and related services.
Respond to your inquiries and provide customer support.
Communicate updates, promotional materials, or information about features (with your consent).
Analyze and monitor usage to enhance the Product experience.
3. Sharing of Information
We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to outside parties except as described below:

Service Providers: We may share your information with third-party service providers who assist us in operating the Product or conducting business activities.
Legal Requirements: We may disclose your information if required to do so by law or in response to valid requests by public authorities.
Business Transfers: In the event of a merger, acquisition, or asset sale, your information may be transferred to the acquiring entity.
4. Data Retention
We will retain your personal information only for as long as is necessary for the purposes set out in this Privacy Notice. We will also retain and use your information as required to comply with our legal obligations, resolve disputes, and enforce our agreements.

5. Your Rights
Depending on your jurisdiction, you may have the following rights regarding your personal information:

Access, update, or delete the personal data we hold about you.
Restrict or object to our processing of your personal data.
Data portability, allowing you to request a copy of your personal data in a structured, machine-readable format.
To exercise any of these rights, please contact us at:
Email: website [at] glitchedfox [dot] studio

6. Security of Data
We take the security of your data seriously and implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect it. However, please note that no method of transmission over the internet or method of electronic storage is 100% secure.

7. Changes to This Privacy Notice
We may update this Privacy Notice from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated "Effective Date." Your continued use of the Product after any changes constitutes your acceptance of the revised notice.

8. Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Notice or our data practices, please contact us at:

Email: website [at] glitchedfox [dot] studio
